    - Implements rate limiting and circuit breakers
    - Identifies itself via User-Agent headers
    - Caches results to minimize repeated requests
    - Sanitizes content to prevent prompt injection

    However, some websites may prohibit automated access in their
    Terms of Service. Users are solely responsible for ensuring their
